text: Please DO NOT come to this library so that I can find seats if I come later than 10am. For a Chinese major this is a good place to find our readings and project work stuff.
There is a hot af librarian here. I think I'm in love

There are many Chinese books, but the location is difficult to find, and it is very different from the location shown on the map. It is located next to the parking lot between Xiaolongbao and the Academy of Social Sciences. You can see it from the small door. It feels very remote and there is no special sign.
